data.description: Welcome to luxury living in the sought-after Clover Point subdivision at Belmont Glen, Guyton! This stunning 4 bed, 2.5 bath home boasts exquisite features including an open kitchen with granite countertops, walk in pantry, kitchen island and additional bar top, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the charm of decorative wainscoting in the breakfast room, along with a beautiful subway tile backsplash throughout the kitchen. Ceiling fans throughout ensure comfort, while the master bedroom offers a tray ceiling and en-suite bathroom withDouble vanity, toilet closet, a walk-in shower and separate bath. Enjoy ample storage in the pull down attic as well as the multitude of linen closets strategically placed throughout. Additional highlights include upper laundry suite (w/d included), walk-in closets, and spacious rooms. Step outside to a the fenced yard and back patio. Plus, enjoy neighborhood amenities in this beautiful community. Don't miss out on this exceptional property!
